name: Contemporary McLEGO Sculpture
description:
A contemporary LEGO representation of the well branded, well recognised Mc Donald's Logo. 

Red background made from LEGO bricks, with the recognisable yellow "M", centrally embossed with black-strip bricks as a shadow area.

Made by artist and sculptor Aaron Keogh.

Made from 46 pieces of real LEGO.

Measures 13 x 18 LEGO pins.

Dimensions: 14.5cm x 10.3cm.

LIMITED EDITION: Only 1 of these will ever be made!! 

(If you go-ahead and buy the sculpture, you can request some money off Mc Donalds coupons from me to be delivered along with the sculpture, so that you can enjoy it on a McFull stomach!!)
